IndividualApplnParticipant.name: IndividualApplnParticipant
IndividualApplnParticipant.description: Represents information about a user or group of participants who have access to a individual application.

Comments.description: The comments about why the participant has access to the individual application.

IndividualApplicationId.description: The individual application associated with the individual application participant.

IsParticipantActive.description: Indicates whether the individual application participant is currently active (true) or not (false).

LastReferencedDate.description: The timestamp for when the current user last viewed a record related to this record.

LastViewedDate.description: The timestamp for when the current user last viewed this record.

Name.description: The name of the individual application participant.

ParticipantId.description: The participant associated with the individual application.

ParticipantRoleId.description: The participant role associated with the individual application participant.
